| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5971 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1d649f87-1c83-5f4f-bbf4-b07f41716767"
